    • purchase

      public boolean purchase​(Client u, PaymentMethod p)
      Makes the purchase of this ticket by client u and payment method p. If it works correctly, a pdf will be generated.
      Parameters:
      u - buyer
      p - payment method
      Returns:
      true if the purchase is successful. False if the ticket is not available or if the payment is not successful.
